Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束在异世界 锡菲罗痛苦的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 龙咲海 与狮堂光、凤凰寺风三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在充满回忆的东京塔 被召唤到锡菲罗去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只这样 想得到锡菲罗的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧多札姆 奇杰达 法连 三个国家还举兵进攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是另外还有一个 来路不明的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲着锡菲罗而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是迪波尼亚与 长得跟小光一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做新星的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们到底是什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风赢得了 与飞鸟公主的射箭比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被阿斯克特给救了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然勉强逃离敌人魔手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小光还在新星手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第37话 复活吧！小光的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须赶快回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩戒之风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 放开我 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把我的衣服与防具还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我用了这么粗暴的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟小姐 为什么会来锡菲罗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为成为支柱的话 就无所不能了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说锡菲罗的公主是 金发蓝眼的美丽公主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为锡菲罗的公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以变得那么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在这样子就很可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要变得更可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果成为支柱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可以喜欢人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗的支柱 必需独自一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撑国家的和平与秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能爱上国家以外的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能让自己获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道锡菲罗现在的状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你成为支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中有点迷惑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗就会很容易地崩溃 变成那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得看到她那么严肃的表情 不知道她们在谈什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须回去城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有闯入者！把他抓起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个以后再说 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我要你再留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次碰面时 我们再喝茶慢慢聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我来喝茶的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来救我的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会把我最重要的人 交给任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩戒之…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被她逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在城堡避难的圣兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请他来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是受伤的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没生气的人 会露出这种表情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你有个三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我会多难过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就没有想过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也该想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一你出事 我会多伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我…请你不要冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光喜欢的东西 我全部都讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小光讨厌自己 所以我最喜欢小光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…讨厌自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 让我们永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看外面了 只要陪我玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起你的愿望！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉过我 就算牺牲生命 也要让剑复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起那个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为何而战的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不让你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去同伴的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去等我的人们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我与 我最重要的人们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀死小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作起来 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 小海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 你怎么了 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的软弱会增强我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们变得多强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量来源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是锡菲罗的人们的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险！阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像帮上你一点点忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人是谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护之风
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法骑士 不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快与我的心同调
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同调？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把心交给我吧 小海 小风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  那个导师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫 古列夫 古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海  幸好你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们做什么都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗很快就会属于我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:24.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如吹越广大海洋的风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:32.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的梦放出数不清的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:35.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不管任何时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:39.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,执意隐藏起受伤的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:43.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,迎向明天的白色背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:47.35,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,令我再也看不下去
